Class LevelThresholdConditionalObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.logevents.observers.LevelThresholdConditionalObserver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LogEventObserver

    public class LevelThresholdConditionalObserver
extends java.lang.Object
implements LogEventObserver
    A LogEventObserver that forwards all log events to a delegate observer if they have a log level equal to or more severe than the threshold.
    Author:
    Johannes Brodwall
